{"tid":2010261,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黑警唔戴口罩話記者冇防疫意識","createTime":"2020-05-10T09:56:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T13:05:31.000Z","uid":19287,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6c28cecf2e374f328546f6dd68984a6fbda37463","tid":2010261,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T09:56:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/579827748716829/posts/3264025900296987/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F579827748716829%2Fposts%2F3264025900296987%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=18ndJK2uCT0lbSM6MbdNQj%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=d597d2fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/579827748716829/posts/3264025900296987/?d=n</a><br />\n【5.10 有警員於荃灣廣場巡查時未配戴口罩】<br />\n<br />\n警方早前進入荃灣廣場內巡查時，有警員未有適當地配戴口罩，無視疫情風險。但同時卻訓斥現場記者，指其違反限聚令及沒有防疫意識，又強調記者沒有特權，更同時大聲向市民喝令離開。記者甚至能看見該名警員有大量口水飛沫噴向市民，極為不衛生。<br />\n<br />\n攝 / Jimmy Lam @ USP United Social Press 社媒<br />\n<br />\n#USP #USP20200510 #武漢肺炎 #限聚令 #荃灣廣場<br />\n<br />\n【新設】USP Instagram account：<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/uspunitedsocialpress/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fuspunitedsocialpress%2F&d=18ndJK2uCT0lbSM6MbdNQj%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=1a781b3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/uspunitedsocialpress/</a><br />\n【新設】USP Twitter account： <a href=\"https://twitter.com/USPhongkong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUSPhongkong&d=18ndJK2uCT0lbSM6MbdNQj%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=3d7331e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/USPhongkong</a><br />\nUSP Telegram Channel： <a href=\"https://t.me/USP_United_Social_Press\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FUSP_United_Social_Press&d=18ndJK2uCT0lbSM6MbdNQj%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=e36c162b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/USP_United_Social_Press</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3z